OL,3,CHomes evacuated and rail services
OL,4,Cdisrupted after gas leak
OL,6,FRail services through Andover and
OL,7,FSalisbury could be disrupted until
OL,8,FThursday afternoon following a gas
OL,9,Fleak near the tracks.
OL,11,FSomeone digging off London Road in
OL,12,FSalisbury caused a gas pipe to rupture
OL,13,Fon Wednesday afternoon.
OL,15,FAn 80 metre cordon was put in place as
OL,16,Fa precaution which meant 75 people
OL,17,Fwere forced to move to safety.
OL,18,FResidents returned to their homes
OL,19,Fovernight.
