OL,3,CHomes evacuated and rail services
OL,4,Cdisrupted after gas leak
OL,6,FThree fire crews, two from Salisbury
OL,7,Fand one from Wilton, were called to
OL,8,Fthe scene after being advised of the
OL,9,Fleak by SGN.
OL,11,FDorset & Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService said that water carriers from
OL,13,FAndover and Wilton and an incident
OL,14,Fcommand vehicle from Devizes were also
OL,15,Fsent to the scene.
OL,17,FLondon Road was closed between the A30/
OL,18,FA338 roundabout and the Hampton Park
OL,19,Froundabout, but this has since been
OL,20,Freopened.
