OL,6,FHowever, the railway line remains
OL,7,Fwithin the reduced cordon and
OL,8,Ftherefore has to stay closed until SGN
OL,9,Fhave made the repair safe.
OL,11,FInformation for affected travellers,
OL,12,Fincluding commuters and students, can
OL,13,Fbe found on .
OL,15,FThe company warned of possible issues
OL,16,Fwith mobile phone coverage in the area
OL,17,Faround the leak, as two masts were
OL,18,Fclosed down temporarily as a safety
OL,19,Fmeasure.
