OL,3,CHomes evacuated and rail services
OL,4,Cdisrupted after gas leak
OL,6,FAnyone in the immediate area may still
OL,7,Fbe able to smell gas in the air, so
OL,8,Fthe advice remains to stay indoors and
OL,9,Fkeep doors and windows closed.
OL,11,FA statement on the South Western
OL,12,FRailway website reads: "Due to a gas
OL,13,Fleak caused by damage by a third party
OL,14,Fnear the railway between Andover and
OL,15,FSalisbury all lines are blocked.
OL,17,F"Train services running through these
OL,18,Fstations may be cancelled, delayed or
OL,19,Frevised. Disruption is expected until
OL,20,F14:30 18/04.
